OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry and fine with
OL,6,Fhazy sunshine. Some patchy low cloud
OL,7,Fmay linger along the coast through the
OL,8,Fday. Cooler along the coast in the
OL,9,Fonshore breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry, with some late
OL,12,Fevening sunshine away from the coast.
OL,13,FOvernight the patchy low cloud may
OL,14,Fspread inland, with some hill fog
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAn outbreak of showers is
OL,18,Fpossible early in the morning, with
OL,19,Fany low cloud or hill fog quickly
OL,20,Fclearing away. Then another dry day
OL,21,Fwith sunny intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
