OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Friday, though isolated showers
OL,7,Fare possible. A band of patchy rain
OL,8,Fmoving in on Saturday, perhaps heavy
OL,9,Fand persistent overnight. Unsettled
OL,10,Fwith showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
